{"tid":2496283,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"香港暫時好成功嘅創作歌手","createTime":"2021-04-19T16:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T17:16:28.000Z","uid":340278,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"91e3f0f842aa9758544d9e62a01e9bce6f10aa88","tid":2496283,"uid":340278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:54:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>定義就係佢作嘅好多歌令好多樂迷都耳熟能祥嘅，除咗自創亦唱得嘅創作歌手</strong>  而且喺買歌曲唱嘅年代，能夠有本土創作係比較難得嘅事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時就係得呢三個創作歌手：<br />\n<br />\n1.許冠傑。香港樂壇始祖，堅持本土嘅第一人，唔洗解釋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.黃家駒。大地 海闊天空 光輝歲月 長城 真的愛你等等 。堅持本土嘅另一人，連羅大佑都認可嘅本地創作歌手，唔洗多講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.陳百強。漣漪 喝采 戀愛預告 深愛着你 偏偏喜歡你等等。聽講唔識音譜都可以創作好多耳熟能祥嘅歌係真天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，又唔洗多講。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時就得咁多，仲有冇異議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115ff8f9f19ebedb4f36d3ba785d05ff54ffe39f","tid":2496283,"uid":1627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"你都係想引人講謙爺啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0debc8b765a1adbfd23959b1a07136c0e29870","tid":2496283,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:55:32.000Z","msg":"韓椊亮都冇人講?"},{"pid":"d4a5cf828303eaaab7e42ba1b44cb35781632cde","tid":2496283,"uid":340278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"115ff8f9f19ebedb4f36d3ba785d05ff54ffe39f","tid":2496283,"uid":1627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"你都係想引人講謙爺啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:57:23.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢係唔錯嘅創作歌手但唔敢吹棒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會害佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw可以提佢嘅"},{"pid":"e363f99078dc0c8a6872a7028bdab5a4ab34cbd2","tid":2496283,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"115ff8f9f19ebedb4f36d3ba785d05ff54ffe39f","tid":2496283,"uid":1627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"你都係想引人講謙爺啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T17:02:04.000Z","msg":"佢事實做幕後真係會好d<br />\n佢唱歌唔係人人接受到"},{"pid":"4a8ea11734f4deed908e2b6c03bec966e6dffccf","tid":2496283,"uid":94931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T17:02:49.000Z","msg":"方大同呢?"},{"pid":"011488f3a5cb557b9faa558178ad29f9be4c6528","tid":2496283,"uid":108269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T17:16:28.000Z","msg":"側田都冇"}]}